What is PHP-FTP-Class
======================

A PHP class to allow easy FTP/FTPS access. This does not allow SFTP connections (SSH).

Doesn't rely on PHPs default FTP functions and also allows FTPs connections which the inbuilt FTP functions are not compatible with.

For more information visit: http://shanerutter.co.uk

